# RELEASE GOAL

Version 1.0 must allow an inventor to:

✓ Create an invention

✓ Upload documents

✓ Receive autonomous analysis

✓ Progress through invention stages

✓ Receive department-generated deliverables

✓ Manage invention history

✓ Review executive summaries

✓ Reach manufacturing readiness

without requiring technical knowledge.

