# PROMPT STANDARD

Every implementation prompt should begin with:

"Continue Project Atlas development.

Treat this Master Plan as the authoritative project roadmap.

Preserve all existing architecture.

Do not rewrite completed systems.

Implement only the next unfinished milestone.

Maintain backward compatibility.

Run all tests.

Report exactly what was completed, what changed, and what remains."

====================================================================

# FINAL OBJECTIVE

Atlas Version 1.0 is complete when an inventor can:

Create an invention.

Validate it.

Research patents.

Analyze competitors.

Determine pricing.

Generate product specifications.

Prepare manufacturing.

Develop branding.

Generate marketing.

Prepare licensing.

Prepare investor materials.

Plan launch.

Track progress.

Receive executive guidance.

All while Atlas performs the majority of the work autonomously and only requests human input when absolutely necessary.

